ockquote><br />\n<br />\n扣埋mpf萬四，一星期48小時"},{"pid":"b45413025250885277665a086cca4d313e3119f7","tid":400500,"uid":25793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頂左一年都頂到梗係邊搵邊做啦傻佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做左半年已經係到諗做夠一年就走算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68bfee7a250e4d9cca0185e5addc45f290058a3","tid":400500,"uid":25793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>更係唔好裸啦，裸左會抖，抖到唔想做野返工，一路比人問候一路揾啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家啲朋友就係咁問我做咩裸辭，雖然係關心，但都忍唔住同佢講之前你都成年廢青啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a9c54eb0a8b506cf294bf5f2c16b733bfdc658","tid":400500,"uid":25793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇吓頂唔頂到？<br />\n頂唔順就寧願辭咗先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n辭左又要後悔wtf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}